Summary: Driving west on liberty grove saw seashell golden aura ufo go into a portal
divs: Sighting Details32.933727, -96.539800 Is the exact cords of the ufo I was heading west on liberty grove i looked up to my right while i was in my car This object was hovering about 40 feet above the power lines it looked like a sea shell with a gyroscope in the center It was golden and had a luminescent golden haze to it. A white hole opened up in front of it and it flew into it and the portal closed. Very interesting i wish i could of recorded it but it was only about 20 seconds plus i was driving. There was other cars around me im pretty sure they saw it too.
